label: Cardiganshire Constabulary register of criminals

metadata.value: Register of criminals apprehended by Cardiganshire Constabulary, 1897-1933 with physical descriptions of prisoners and details of previous convictions. Photographs are included of most of those sentenced between 1897 and 1909.

value.@value: This content has been digitised by the National Library of Wales
